                        <interp inst="t18690712-630-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted in March</hi>, 1865, <hi rend="italic">to which he</hi>
               </p>
